'''No Time To Die''' ni filime yo gusetsa no gukundana yo muri [[Gana]] yo mu 2006 yakozwe na Wolfgang Panzer, Umudage, umwanditsi akaba n'umuyobozi  kandi yayikoranye na King Ampaw, igihembo yatsindiye nk'umuyobozi akaba n'umukinnyi wa [[Gana]]<ref>https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/no-time-to-die</ref>.  Filime yari iyobowe na King Ampaw. Umuziki wahimbwe na Ben Michael Mankhamba umucuranzi wa gitari wa Malawi, umuririmbyi, umwanditsi w'indirimbo,<ref>https://deadline.com/2021/11/no-time-to-die-mgm-sets-pvod-release-date-1234869456/</ref>.  Imyambarire yateguwe na Lisa Meier. Yakozwe mu 2006 muri [[Gana]] no mu [[Budage]]<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/no-time-to-die/</ref>.   Ni firime ivuga icyongereza imara iminota 95.  Yatoranijwe mu Kuboza 2016 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime rya [[Afurika]] Diaspora (ADIFF) i New York<ref>https://www.africanfilm.com/products/no-time-to-die</ref>. 

== Ikibanza ==
Asante, umushoferi utwara imodoka zo gushyingura muri [[Gana]], akeneye uwo bashakanye ariko akazi ke gakanga abadamu benshi<ref>https://www.laboutiqueafricavivre.com/films/463-no-time-to-die-4260152390114.html</ref>. Atangira kureba  umukiriya (Esi) wapfushije nyina, akamenya uburyo bwo kumuganiriza<ref>https://cines.com/en/film/no-time-to-die-2006</ref>. ariko se akabuza uwo mubano kagati ya Esi na Asante. Asante arakomeza ahinduka umushoferi wambere wimodoka yo gushyingura i Accra ubashije kurongora <ref>https://mubi.com/films/no-time-to-die</ref>. Iyi filime yari iyo gusobanura umuco nyafurika werekana impinduka mumigenzo yo gushyingura abanyafurika kubera ingaruka zabakoloni muri [[Afrika]]<ref>https://www.filmfrasor.no/en/film/2008/no-time-to-die</ref>. 

